title: Ep 78: Stop Being all Fu$%ed up!
description: Have you heard of Dan Pena, the 50 Billion Dollar Man and Motivational Speaker? He tells it like it is and this week I explore the world of Pena. Do you work 20 hours a day, 7 days a week? Do you not have friends that are LOSERS? Then you may become a billionaire too! Is it possible to be successful and still hang out? Let's get deep on it, bros.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
